              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<h2><strong>Level Up Your Inventory: Bulk Custom Playmats for Your Business<\/strong><\/h2><h4>Are you looking for a high-quality, high-margin product to delight your customers? Whether you're a local business or a professional creator, custom playmats are a sought-after accessory in the gaming world. We offer a premium, hassle-free way to design and order custom playmats in bulk.<\/h4>",
