                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p><strong>Who Can Benefit from Bulk Playmat Orders?<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Local Game Stores (LGSs)<\/strong>: Stock up on branded store mats, exclusive tournament prizes, or mats featuring local artist designs to drive traffic and build community spirit.<\/li><li><strong>Artists<\/strong>: Turn your incredible digital or traditional art into a functional, collectible product to sell directly to your fans and diversify your income streams.<\/li><li><strong>Vendors & Event Organizers<\/strong>: Create unique merchandise for conventions, trade shows, or large-scale gaming events, giving attendees a memorable takeaway they'll actually use.<\/li><\/ul>",
