            "text_bLXKMw": {
              "type": "text",
              "name": "t:names.text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p><strong>The Value of Bulk Buying<\/strong><\/p><p>Ordering custom playmats in volume isn't just about saving money—it's about growing your business:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Increased Margins:<\/strong> A lower per-unit cost directly translates into higher profits when you sell the mats at retail price.<\/li><li><strong>Stock Your Shelves:<\/strong> Ensure you always have popular designs and core products in stock for your customers, preventing lost sales.<\/li><li><strong>Exclusive Products: <\/strong>Offer unique, limited-edition merchandise available only from you to build brand loyalty and create buzz.<\/li><li><strong>Professional Quality:<\/strong> We use high-quality materials, vibrant, fade-resistant printing, and a smooth, durable surface to ensure every mat meets professional standards. Your customers will notice the difference.<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Get Started Today!<\/strong><\/p><p>We handle the production details so you can focus on the design and selling. We offer fast turnaround times and quality control on every order.<\/p><p>Ready to see the quality for yourself? You can request a <strong>sample playmat<\/strong> for just <strong>$10<\/strong> to feel the material, check the print clarity, and ensure your designs look exactly as you expect before committing to a bulk order.<\/p>",
                "width": "100%",
                "max_width": "none",
                "alignment": "left",
                "type_preset": "custom",
                "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                "font_size": "1rem",
